    "en": {
      "title": "Separate regulation for use of two-wheelers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thus, it has been decided to set aside separate rules for those who use two-wheelers in areas covered by the Colombo Municipal Council.",
        "The first phase of the operation is planned to be implemented next week for the use of the Marunga Bicycle through Amer Road, Hetiawat and the Colombo Harbor entrance. (a)"
      ],
